  "description": "<i>Producent Boubli</i> is a simulation managerial game. The player controls factory by setting a weekly production schedule, hiring and firing workers, fulfillment orders, determining wages and prices of goods. The game allows to take a loan and features various random encounters. Unhappy workers may go for a strike, higher prices cause a reduction in orders. The game ends when the player earns one million dollars or bankrupt.",
